{
  "stem": "24625.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was fun.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yiddish, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I spoke good Yiddish, but I couldn't read or write.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my mother was reading to me, and I had to remember everything by memory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I did pretty good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I was going to school to learn how to read.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in the beginning, I couldn't read the Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So everything by memory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This I remember was the good years, that's for sure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I never met my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were alive but in Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I never went back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mom went back once in '35, I think, and took my sister.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't want to go, so I stayed with my dad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I never went to Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in '41 because the Belgian underground contacted the Jewish family and said that they're rounding up-- they're starting to round up the Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they don't want that the all Jewish children should disappear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They cannot protect every adult, but at least let them protect the children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So whoever wanted to, they gave away their children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you had to sign a paper that you couldn't see them or anything for the safety of the children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my parents gave us away, all three of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was in 1941.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from '41 to '44, I never saw them anymore, my parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Describe to me how it-- you know, the whole way that it happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who came to talk to you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How it happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first time I went to the school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I stayed there a couple of months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, we didn't go back to-- we didn't go back home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went back to a home it called-- in Brussels it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[FRENCH], J-O-C, the Youth of Catholic Children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took care.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
